{"type": "article", "id": 21893, "title": "比利时品牌valerie_objects的餐具项目", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-04T07:30:12Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 41, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702115140neVr60sQ3TlhfE4c.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">比利时的一家新品牌 valerie_objects 在巴黎家具博览会上推出了一套餐具项目，他们邀请多位设计师重新设计这些生活中常见的餐具。日本设计师二俣公一（koichi futatsumata）将手柄设计成凸出的八角形，两端连接依然是片状的，有雕塑感。 wieki somers工作室的餐具手柄是中空的，像是将金属折叠起来。荷兰设计师 maarten baas 则走向精致的反面，餐具的形状更随意，尤其是切刀的刀口并不规整，增加了一份天然和自在。<a href=\"http://www.valerie-objects.com/Product/The_Cutlery_Project/\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115137JBaGEzXUT6If3MHn.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.2799511\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115137BTKvJzChV1s98o2A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7799511\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115138uAsnxKHI61MrYpN3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76894866\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021151386eXfgMHztZlP5cVq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.77506112\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115139dODcyMR7W4FJzCKS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n"}